er use cases that require high transaction throughput.StarkWare has attracted notable partnerships and investments from industry leaders such as Intel, Pantera Capital, and Coinbase. Their technology has also been successfully implemented and tested in collaboration with various organizations, including DeversiFi, one of the largest decentralized exchanges.Overall, StarkWare is playing a key role in addressing scalability challenges in the blockchain space and enabling the adoption of decentralized applications on a global scale."
